0T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"0分重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2835529ecc3ab6f50f6fd402de6f3349c068bcb6","tid":483142,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>欣賞你去改詞 <br />\n<br />\n但係改完既詞既意境<span style=\"color: red;\">就同你呢刻一樣</span><br />\n<br />\n無意義 隨便湊出語句當了事 <br />\n<br />\n唔知想點 好奇怪</blockquote><br />\n呢句好有意境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b884b5b2b313bf2d94206e5dd8fd7b43aa8896f","tid":483142,"uid":37464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636bb3b37e8d19ea70e33d9acf8cd77cd58779de","tid":483142,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>0分重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32249eb1675ab5e7ac82a004aa7571b9ae3cf3b5","tid":483142,"uid":103514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:31:03.000Z","msg":"如果單睇歌詞，根本無一啲非「詞人」不可嘅意象同情境。例如，我將首歌改名叫&laquo;作家&raquo;一樣可以。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，啲詞扣唔實歌名<br />\n<br />\n可以先諗一啲有關「詞人」嘅特性，例如：<br />\n-苦苦思量<br />\n-寫別人/自己故事<br />\n-(多數)獨自創作&gt;&gt;孤單<br />\n-字數內容隨旋律決定&gt;&gt;被動&gt;&gt;如同愛情中兩者關係<br />\n<br />\n然後就可以再根據以上特性入詞<br />\n<br />\n另外，嘗試主歌多啲日常/ 生活化嘅描述，增強聽眾共鳴<br />\n<br />\n副歌hook line要夠記憶性強，一聽就記到<br />\n(依家太簡單)"},{"pid":"b0803df1c20e8cdc011208168f4321bb65221d2e","tid":483142,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff91e394d8a2fd6d175f686305407e0072d0546","tid":483142,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果單睇歌詞，根本無一啲非「詞人」不可嘅意象同情境。例如，我將首歌改名叫&laquo;作家&raquo;一樣可以。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，啲詞扣唔實歌名<br />\n<br />\n可以先諗一啲有關「詞人」嘅特性，例如：<br />\n-苦苦思量<br />\n-寫別人/自己故事<br />\n-(多數)獨自創作&gt;&gt;孤單<br />\n-<span style=\"color: red;\">字數內容隨旋律決定&gt;&gt;被動&gt;&gt;如同愛情中兩者關係</span><br />\n<br />\n然後就可以再根據以上特性入詞<br />\n<br />\n另外，嘗試主歌多啲日常/ 生活化嘅描述，增強聽眾共鳴<br />\n<br />\n副歌hook line要夠記憶性強，一聽就記到<br />\n(依家太簡單)</blockquote><br />\n除咗呢樣其他套落作家都得啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bfdcaf2ea2656bf049760fba742df9dad33743","tid":483142,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"詞ok 但唱個個好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc6b990b12d1d0c5738be761e1d1f1730d53b25","tid":483142,"uid":37464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T09:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果單睇歌詞，根本無一啲非「詞人」不可嘅意象同情境。例如，我將首歌改名叫&laquo;作家&raquo;一樣可以。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，啲詞扣唔實歌名<br />\n<br />\n可以先諗一啲有關「詞人」嘅特性，例如：<br />\n-苦苦思量<br />\n-寫別人/自己故事<br />\n-(多數)獨自創作&gt;&gt;孤單<br />\n-字數內容隨旋律決定&gt;&gt;被動&gt;&gt;如同愛情中兩者關係<br />\n<br />\n然後就可以再根據以上特性入詞<br />\n<br />\n另外，嘗試主歌多啲日常/ 生活化嘅描述，增強聽眾共鳴<br />\n<br />\n副歌hook line要夠記憶性強，一聽就記到<br />\n(依家太簡單)</blockquote><br />\n如果講詞人特性，其實份詞都算有<br />\n最明顯是強調自己的作品要按監製意願修改，無力反抗，呢樣反而係作家無既特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。乃至第一句填數字，所謂的0243已經係填詞技巧之一。<br />\n<br />\n另外，其實原詞叫演員，佢同樣唔係講緊演員。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb060fc3530dddcd6c9e0d5f4730b32ae419de0b","tid":483142,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326cd3a550da9d6632b4b5442b30fd4dfd96fc94","tid":483142,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a00e60e53a312557ca35639db64da7831e1a019","tid":483142,"uid":50647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果單睇歌詞，根本無一啲非「詞人」不可嘅意象同情境。例如，我將首歌改名叫&laquo;作家&raquo;一樣可以。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，啲詞扣唔實歌名<br />\n<br />\n可以先諗一啲有關「詞人」嘅特性，例如：<br />\n-苦苦思量<br />\n-寫別人/自己故事<br />\n-(多數)獨自創作&gt;&gt;孤單<br />\n-字數內容隨旋律決定&gt;&gt;被動&gt;&gt;如同愛情中兩者關係<br />\n<br />\n然後就可以再根據以上特性入詞<br />\n<br />\n另外，嘗試主歌多啲日常/ 生活化嘅描述，增強聽眾共鳴<br />\n<br />\n副歌hook line要夠記憶性強，一聽就記到<br />\n(依家太簡單)</blockquote><br />\n如果講詞人特性，其實份詞都算有<br />\n最明顯是強調自己的作品要按監製意願修改，無力反抗，呢樣反而係作家無既特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。乃至第一句填數字，所謂的0243已經係填詞技巧之一。<br />\n<br />\n另外，其實原詞叫演員，佢同樣唔係講緊演員。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比喻緊拍緊拖但另一半有好多野收收埋埋似演員喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7192a1d632708d3ab74d02cae93d34484de23c","tid":483142,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果單睇歌詞，根本無一啲非「詞人」不可嘅意象同情境。例如，我將首歌改名叫&laquo;作家&raquo;一樣可以。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，啲詞扣唔實歌名<br />\n<br />\n可以先諗一啲有關「詞人」嘅特性，例如：<br />\n-苦苦思量<br />\n-寫別人/自己故事<br />\n-(多數)獨自創作&gt;&gt;孤單<br />\n-字數內容隨旋律決定&gt;&gt;被動&gt;&gt;如同愛情中兩者關係<br />\n<br />\n然後就可以再根據以上特性入詞<br />\n<br />\n另外，嘗試主歌多啲日常/ 生活化嘅描述，增強聽眾共鳴<br />\n<br />\n副歌hook line要夠記憶性強，一聽就記到<br />\n(依家太簡單)</blockquote><br />\n如果講詞人特性，其實份詞都算有<br />\n最明顯是強調自己的作品要按監製意願修改，無力反抗，呢樣反而係作家無既特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。乃至第一句填數字，所謂的0243已經係填詞技巧之一。<br />\n<br />\n另外，其實原詞叫演員，佢同樣唔係講緊演員。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比喻緊拍緊拖但另一半有好多野收收埋埋似演員喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我當然明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我指演員既[特性]"},{"pid":"28d8a9d3543f743e16944f85735aec03d4d8b31d","tid":483142,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2815b0f354bf00f6e86dc19595edfedd0e91f20e","tid":483142,"uid":86962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"如果把聲再佬味d就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed52cd3b5eab1c9d50e380985702ca8680bba329","tid":483142,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T23:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果把聲再佬味d就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個味道或者仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90087482dd8e7cefa8488f9cd586534cad830b05","tid":483142,"uid":64144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:15:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得樓主係有心寫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我聽完就無乜感覺，<br />\n<br />\n啲音有啲格硬泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ea8a51d90c68a69a9f9a9847a686b67d97502c","tid":483142,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得樓主係有心寫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br